🏠 Unlock the Mystery of Home Buying! 🗝️✨

Are you ready to take the leap into homeownership but find yourself puzzled by the terms 'Deposit' and 'Down Payment'? Let's clear the air! 🌬️

🔑 Deposit: This is your first step after your offer gets the nod! 🤝 It's part of your down payment and shows the seller you mean business. It's not just money; it's a promise! 💰📜

🔑 Down Payment: Think of this as the grand finale at the closing stage! 🎉 It's a chunk of the home's price (minimum 5%, dream for 20%) that you pay upfront. And guess what? Going 20% or above might save you from mortgage default insurance! 💸🏡

🌟 Don't let these terms intimidate you. As your South San Francisco realty expert, I'm here to guide you every step of the way. Slide into my DMs for more insights and let's turn your home dreams into reality! 🌈🏠
